00:28:46,920 --> 00:28:48,790
Kebetulan aku punya satu permintaan.

312
00:28:49,070 --> 00:28:50,110
Silakan Nona Lin katakan.

313
00:28:51,440 --> 00:28:54,000
Kalau kelak aku ingin meminta bantuanmu,

314
00:28:54,200 --> 00:28:55,310
