320
00:29:26,590 --> 00:29:28,000
Kasus ini sudah ditutup.

321
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:29,790
Sudah ditutup?

322
00:29:30,550 --> 00:29:32,270
Barusan Wu Zhuo dan Kepala Penjaga Qian

323
00:29:32,270 --> 00:29:33,400
